-- raw sql results do not include filled-in values for 'shipments.assigned_week'


-- use existing shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVLVN1657216617755_shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered
-- use existing shipment_current_assignment in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV1E41657217050284_shipment_current_assignment
-- use existing shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg in LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV64A1657141088092_shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_ag
SELECT * FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z___pivot_row_rank, RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY z__pivot_col_rank ORDER BY z___min_rank) as z__pivot_col_ordering, CASE WHEN z___min_rank = z___rank THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS z__is_highest_ranked_cell FROM (
SELECT *, MIN(z___rank) OVER (PARTITION BY "shipper_lanes.lane_city_state","shipper_applications.name","shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_type","shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_target","shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_type","shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_target") as z___min_rank FROM (
SELECT *, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN (CASE WHEN "sssaa.pickup_weighted_on_time_percent" IS NOT NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) ELSE 2 END, CASE WHEN z__pivot_col_rank=1 THEN "sssaa.pickup_weighted_on_time_percent" ELSE NULL END DESC, "sssaa.pickup_weighted_on_time_percent" DESC, z__pivot_col_rank, "shipper_lanes.lane_city_state", "shipper_applications.name", "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_type", "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_target", "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_type", "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_target") AS z___rank FROM (
SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "shipments.assigned_week" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "shipments.assigned_week") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST((TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', shipment_current_assignment.created_second ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'))::timestamp_ntz  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS "shipments.assigned_week",
    ((nullif(initcap(shipper_lanes.pickup_city::varchar), ''))||', '||(nullif(shipper_lanes.pickup_state_code, '')))||' > '||((nullif(initcap(shipper_lanes.delivery_city::varchar), ''))||', '||(nullif(shipper_lanes.delivery_state_code, '')))  AS "shipper_lanes.lane_city_state",
    shipper_applications.name  AS "shipper_applications.name",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_PICK_UP_MINUTE_HOUR_DAY_", 'Day')  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_type",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_PICK_UP_",.95)  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_target",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_DELIVERY_MINUTE_HOUR_DAY_", 'Day')  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_type",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_DELIVERY_",.95)  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_target",
        SUM((shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.pickup_arrived_count) * (shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.pickup_on_time_percent)) / nullif(SUM(shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.pickup_arrived_count), 0) AS "sssaa.pickup_weighted_on_time_percent",
        SUM((shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.delivery_arrived_count) * (shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.delivery_on_time_percent)) / nullif(SUM(shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.delivery_arrived_count), 0) AS "sssaa.delivery_weighted_on_time_percent",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_rates  AS shipper_rates
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.dates  AS dates ON (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(dates."ACTUAL_DATE"::varchar::timestamp_ntz ), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) between (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(shipper_rates.start_date ), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) and (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(shipper_rates.end_date ), 'YYYY-MM-DD'))
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVLVN1657216617755_shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered AS shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered ON shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered.shipper_rate_id=shipper_rates.id and
        date_trunc('day', shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered.appointment_end_at)=(TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(dates."ACTUAL_DATE"::varchar::timestamp_ntz ), 'YYYY-MM-DD'))

LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments ON shipments.id=shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered.shipment_id and
          --shipments.shipper_application_id=shipper_rates.shipper_application_id and
          shipments.is_tonu = false --and
          --shipments.priced_under_contract

LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV1E41657217050284_shipment_current_assignment AS shipment_current_assignment ON shipment_current_assignment.shipment_id=shipments.id
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV64A1657141088092_shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_ag AS shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg ON shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.id=shipments.id
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON shipper_applications.id=shipper_rates.shipper_application_id
LEFT JOIN pc_fivetran_db.google_sheets.shipper_kpis_1  AS shipper_kpi_targets ON (shipper_kpi_targets."STARK_SHIPPER_ID")=shipper_applications.id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_lanes  AS shipper_lanes ON shipper_lanes.id=shipper_rates.transfix_shipper_lane_id
WHERE (((((( (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', shipment_current_assignment.created_second ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'))::timestamp_ntz  ))) >= (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-05-02') AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))) AND ((( (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', shipment_current_assignment.created_second ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'))::timestamp_ntz  ))) < (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-06-28') AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AND (shipper_rates.shipper_application_id not in (2478, 2480, 2514) )
GROUP BY
    (DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST((TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', shipment_current_assignment.created_second ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'))::timestamp_ntz  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))),
    2,
    3,
    4,
    5,
    6,
    7) ww
) bb WHERE z__pivot_col_rank <= 16384
) aa
) xx
) zz
 WHERE (z__pivot_col_rank <= 50 OR z__is_highest_ranked_cell = 1) AND (z___pivot_row_rank <= 50 OR z__pivot_col_ordering = 1) ORDER BY z___pivot_row_rank

-- sql for creating the pivot row totals
SELECT
    ((nullif(initcap(shipper_lanes.pickup_city::varchar), ''))||', '||(nullif(shipper_lanes.pickup_state_code, '')))||' > '||((nullif(initcap(shipper_lanes.delivery_city::varchar), ''))||', '||(nullif(shipper_lanes.delivery_state_code, '')))  AS "shipper_lanes.lane_city_state",
    shipper_applications.name  AS "shipper_applications.name",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_PICK_UP_MINUTE_HOUR_DAY_", 'Day')  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_type",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_PICK_UP_",.95)  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_pickup_target",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_DELIVERY_MINUTE_HOUR_DAY_", 'Day')  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_type",
    coalesce(shipper_kpi_targets."ON_TIME_DELIVERY_",.95)  AS "shipper_kpi_targets.on_time_delivery_target",
        SUM((shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.pickup_arrived_count) * (shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.pickup_on_time_percent)) / nullif(SUM(shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.pickup_arrived_count), 0) AS "sssaa.pickup_weighted_on_time_percent",
        SUM((shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.delivery_arrived_count) * (shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.delivery_on_time_percent)) / nullif(SUM(shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.delivery_arrived_count), 0) AS "sssaa.delivery_weighted_on_time_percent",
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN (CASE WHEN shipments.is_tonu  THEN 1 ELSE 0 END
) = 0 THEN shipments.id  ELSE NULL END) AS "shipments.shipment_count"
FROM stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_rates  AS shipper_rates
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.dates  AS dates ON (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(dates."ACTUAL_DATE"::varchar::timestamp_ntz ), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) between (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(shipper_rates.start_date ), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) and (TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(shipper_rates.end_date ), 'YYYY-MM-DD'))
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YVLVN1657216617755_shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered AS shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered ON shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered.shipper_rate_id=shipper_rates.id and
        date_trunc('day', shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered.appointment_end_at)=(TO_CHAR(TO_DATE(dates."ACTUAL_DATE"::varchar::timestamp_ntz ), 'YYYY-MM-DD'))

LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipments  AS shipments ON shipments.id=shipment_pickup_appointment_tendered.shipment_id and
          --shipments.shipper_application_id=shipper_rates.shipper_application_id and
          shipments.is_tonu = false --and
          --shipments.priced_under_contract

LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV1E41657217050284_shipment_current_assignment AS shipment_current_assignment ON shipment_current_assignment.shipment_id=shipments.id
LEFT JOIN LOOKER_SCRATCH.LR$YV64A1657141088092_shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_ag AS shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg ON shipment_shipment_stop_appointments_agg.id=shipments.id
INNER JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_applications  AS shipper_applications ON shipper_applications.id=shipper_rates.shipper_application_id
LEFT JOIN pc_fivetran_db.google_sheets.shipper_kpis_1  AS shipper_kpi_targets ON (shipper_kpi_targets."STARK_SHIPPER_ID")=shipper_applications.id
LEFT JOIN stark_prod.recreated_tables.shipper_lanes  AS shipper_lanes ON shipper_lanes.id=shipper_rates.transfix_shipper_lane_id
WHERE (((((( (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', shipment_current_assignment.created_second ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'))::timestamp_ntz  ))) >= (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-05-02') AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))) AND ((( (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', shipment_current_assignment.created_second ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'))::timestamp_ntz  ))) < (CONVERT_TIMEZONE('America/New_York', 'UTC', CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP('2022-06-28') AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ)))))) AND (shipper_rates.shipper_application_id not in (2478, 2480, 2514) )

SELECT *, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY CASE WHEN "shipments.assigned_week" IS NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END, "shipments.assigned_week") AS z__pivot_col_rank FROM (
SELECT
    (TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('week', CONVERT_TIMEZONE('UTC', 'America/New_York', CAST((TO_CHAR(DATE_TRUNC('second', shipment_current_assignment.created_second ), 'YYYY-MM-DD HH24:MI:SS'))::timestamp_ntz  AS TIMESTAMP_NTZ))), 'YYYY-MM-DD')) AS "shipments.assigned_week",
